ANSWER-02
INPUT:
<?php
// Set table size
$size = 3;

// Print header row
echo "  ";
for ($col = 1; $col <= $size; $col++) {
    echo "$col ";
}
echo "\n";

// Print division values row by row
for ($row = 1; $row <= $size; $row++) {
    echo "$row ";
    for ($col = 1; $col <= $size; $col++) {
        $result = round($row / $col, 2);
        echo "$result ";
    }
    echo "\n";
}
?>

OUPUT:
  1 2 3 
1 1 0.5 0.33 
2 2 1 0.67 
3 3 1.5 1 


=== Code Execution Successful ===

